titlealts.searchtitle: Data Element: INVASIVE BREAST CANCER GRADE NOT KNOWN (PERCENTAGE OF INVASIVE BREAST CANCERS) - Description

div.p: INVASIVE BREAST CANCER GRADE NOT KNOWN (PERCENTAGE OF INVASIVE BREAST CANCERS) is the percentage of women diagnosed with invasive breast cancer, where the BREAST BIOPSY REFERRAL OUTCOME National Code is 'Positive; i.e. cancer detected - invasive size not known - grade not known' or 'Positive; i.e. cancer detected - invasive size known - grade not known'.
